    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question, i just got a prescription for zolpidem to help me sleep since im struggling lately. i usually have a glass of red wine with dinner tho, is it okay if i take the pill after my wine? i feel like it might actually help me drift off faster if i combine them lol",
